a Coleman]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Marion Roper]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Equestrian==\n{{main|Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics}}\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event}}\n|-\n| Individual [[dressage]]<br />{{DetailsLink|Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual dressage}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Xavier Lesage]] and ''Taine''|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Charles Marion]] and ''Linon''|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Hiram Tuttle (equestrian)|Hiram Tuttle]] and ''Olympic''|USA|1932 Summer}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| Team [[dressage]]<br />{{DetailsLink|Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Team dressage}}\n|{{flagIOCteam|FRA|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Xavier Lesage]] and ''Taine'' <br> [[Charles Marion]] and ''Linon'' <br> [[Andr\u00e9 Jousseaume]] and ''Sorelta''\n|{{flagIOCteam|SWE|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Bertil Sandstr\u00f6m]] and ''Kreta'' <br> [[Thomas Bystr\u00f6m]] and ''Gulliver'' <br> [[Gustaf Adolf Boltenstern, Jr.]] and ''Ingo''\n|{{flagIOCteam|USA|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Hiram Tuttle (equestrian)|Hiram Tuttle]] and ''Olympic'' <br> [[Isaac Kitts]] and ''American Lady'' <br> [[Alvin Moore]] and ''Water Pat''\n|-\n| Individual [[eventing]] <br />{{DetailsLink|Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual eventing}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]] and ''Ferdinand''|NED|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Earl Foster Thomson]] and ''[[Jenny Camp]]''|USA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Clarence von Rosen, Jr.]] and ''Sunnyside Maid''|SWE|1932 Summer}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| Team [[eventing]]<br />{{DetailsLink|Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Team eventing}}\n|{{flagIOCteam|USA|1932 Summer}}<br> [[Earl Foster Thomson]] and ''[[Jenny Camp]]'' <br> [[Harry Chamberlin]] and ''Pleasant Smiles'' <br> [[Edwin Argo]] and ''Honolulu Tomboy''\n|{{flagIOCteam|NED|1932 Summer}}<br> [[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]] and ''Marcroix'' <br> [[Karel Schummelketel]] and ''Duiveltje'' <br> [[Aer