ino Rossi]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Peter J\u00f8rgensen (boxer)|Peter J\u00f8rgensen]]|DEN|1932 Summer}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| [[Heavyweight]]<br>(over 79.4&nbsp;kg/175&nbsp;lb)<br/>{{DetailsLink|Boxing at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's heavyweight}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Santiago Lovell]]|ARG|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Luigi Rovati]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Frederick Feary]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Cycling==\n{{main|Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics}}\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event}}\n|-\n| [[Individual time trial]]<br/>{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's individual road race}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Attilio Pavesi]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Guglielmo Segato]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Bernhard Britz]]|SWE|1932 Summer}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| [[Team time trial]]<br/>{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's team road race}}\n| {{flagIOCteam|ITA|1932 Summer}}<br /> [[Giuseppe Olmo]]<br /> [[Attilio Pavesi]]<br /> [[Guglielmo Segato]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|DEN|1932 Summer}}<br /> [[Henry Hansen (cyclist)|Henry]]<br /> [[Leo Nielsen]]<br /> [[Frode S\u00f8rensen (cyclist)|Frode S\u00f8rensen]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|SWE}}<br /> [[Arne Berg (cyclist)|Arne Berg]]<br /> [[Bernhard Britz]]<br /> [[Sven H\u00f6glund]]\n|-\n| [[Time trial|1000m time trial]]<br />{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 1000 m time trial}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Dunc Gray]]|AUS|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Jacobus van Egmond]]|NED|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Charles Rampelberg]]|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n|-\n| [[Sprint (cycling)|Sprint]]<br />{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's sprint|Sprint}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Jacobus van Egmond]]|NED|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Louis Chaillot]]|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Bruno Pellizzari]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| [[Tandem]]<br />{{Deta