on]] and ''[[Jenny Camp]]'' <br> [[Harry Chamberlin]] and ''Pleasant Smiles'' <br> [[Edwin Argo]] and ''Honolulu Tomboy''\n|{{flagIOCteam|NED|1932 Summer}}<br> [[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]] and ''Marcroix'' <br> [[Karel Schummelketel]] and ''Duiveltje'' <br> [[Aernout van Lennep]] and ''Henk'' \n|''No Bronze awarded''\n|-\n| Individual [[Show jumping|jumping]]<br />{{DetailsLink|Equestrian at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual jumping}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Takeichi Nishi]] and ''Uranus''|JPN|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Harry Chamberlin]] and ''Show Girl''|USA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Clarence von Rosen, Jr.]] and ''Empire''|SWE|1932 Summer}}\n|-\n|}\n*Note:''The scheduled team jumping event was declared void as no nation completed the course with three riders''\n\n==Fencing==\n{{main|Fencing at the 1932 Summer Olympics}}\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event|}}\n|-\n| Men's \u00e9p\u00e9e<br />{{DetailsLink|Fencing at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's \u00e9p\u00e9e}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Giancarlo Cornaggia Medici]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Georges Buchard]]|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Carlo Agostoni]]|ITA|1932 Summer}}\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| Men's team \u00e9p\u00e9e<br />{{DetailsLink|Fencing at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's team \u00e9p\u00e9e}} \n|{{flagIOCteam|FRA|1932 Summer}}<br/>[[Fernand Jourdant]]<br/>[[Bernard Schmetz]]<br/>[[Georges Tainturier]]<br/>[[Georges Buchard]]<br/>[[Jean Piot]]<br/>[[Philippe Cattiau]]\n|{{flagIOCteam|ITA|1932 Summer}}<br/>[[Saverio Ragno]]<br/>[[Giancarlo Cornaggia Medici]]<br/>[[Franco Riccardi]]<br/>[[Carlo Agostoni]]<br/>[[Renzo Minoli]]\n|{{flagIOCteam|USA|1932 Summer}}<br/>[[George Charles Calnan]]<br/>[[Gustave Marinius Heiss]]<br/>[[Frank Stahl Jr. Righeimer]]<br/>[[Tracy Jaeckel]]<br/>[[Curtis Charles Shears]]<br/>[[Miguel Angel De Capriles]]\n|-\n| Men's foil<br />{{DetailsLink|Fencing at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's foil}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[