 Summer}}\n|- valign=top\n| 4&times;200 m freestyle relay<br>{{DetailsLink|Swimming at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 4 \u00d7 200 metre freestyle relay}}\n| {{flagIOCteam|JPN|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Yasuji Miyazaki]]<br>[[Hisakichi Toyoda]]<br>[[Takashi Yokoyama (swimmer)|Takashi Yokoyama]]<br>[[Masanori Yusa]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|USA|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Frank Booth (swimmer)|Frank Booth]]<br>[[George Fissler]]<br>[[Maiola Kalili]]<br>[[Manuella Kalili]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|HUN|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Istv\u00e1n B\u00e1r\u00e1ny]]<br>[[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 Szabados]]<br>[[Andr\u00e1s Sz\u00e9kely]]<br>[[Andr\u00e1s Wani\u00e9]]\n|}\n\n'''Women'''\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event}}\n|-\n| 100 m freestyle<br>{{DetailsLink|Swimming at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 100 metre freestyle}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Helene Madison]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Willy den Ouden]]|NED|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Eleanor Garatti|Eleanor Saville]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n|-\n| 400 m freestyle<br>{{DetailsLink|Swimming at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 400 metre freestyle}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Helene Madison]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Lenore Kight]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Jenny Maakal]]|RSA|1932 Summer}}\n|-\n| 100 m backstroke<br>{{DetailsLink|Swimming at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 100 metre backstroke}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Eleanor Holm]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Bonnie Mealing]]|AUS|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Valerie Davies]]|GBR|1932 Summer}}\n|-\n| 200 m breaststroke<br>{{DetailsLink|Swimming at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 200 metre breaststroke}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Clare Dennis]]|AUS|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Hideko Maehata]]|JPN|1932 Summer}}\n| {{flagIOCmedalist|[[Else Jacobsen]]|DEN|1932 Summer}}\n|- valign=top\n| 4&times;100 m freestyle relay<br>{{DetailsLink|Swimming at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 4 \u00d7 100 metre freestyle relay}}\n| {{flagIOCteam|USA|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Helen Johns (swimmer)|Helen Johns]]<br>[[Helene Madison]]<br>[[Josephine McKim]]<br>[[Eleanor Garatti|Eleanor Saville]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|NED|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Corrie Ladd\u00e9]]<br>[[Willy den Ouden]]<br>[[Puck Oversloot]]<br>[[Maria Vierdag]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|GBR|1932 Summer}}<br>[[Joyce Cooper]]<br>[[Valerie Davies]]<br>[[Edna Hughes]]<br>[[Helen Varcoe]]\n|}\n\n==Water polo==\n{{main|Water polo at the 1932 Summer Olympics}}\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event}}\n|- valign=top\n|Men's tournament<br />{{DetailsLink|Water polo at the 1932 Summer Olympics}}\n| {{flagIOCteam|HUN|1932 Summer}} <br> [[Istv\u00e1n Barta]]<br>[[Gy\u00f6rgy Br\u00f3dy]]<br>[[Oliv\u00e9r Halassy]]<br>[[M\u00e1rton Homonnai]]<br>[[S\u00e1ndor Iv\u00e1dy]]<br>[[Alajos Keser\u0171]]<br>[[Ferenc Keser\u0171]]<br>[[J\u00e1nos N\u00e9meth]]<br>[[Mikl\u00f3s S\u00e1rk\u00e1ny]]<br>[[J\u00f3zsef V\u00e9rtesy]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|GER|1932 Summer}} <br> [[Emil Benecke]]<br>[[Otto Cordes]]<br>[[Hans Eckstein]]<br>[[Fritz Gunst]]<br>[[Erich Rademacher]]<br>[[Joachim Rademacher]]<br>[[Hans Schulze]]<br>[[Heiko Schwartz]]\n| {{flagIOCteam|USA|1932 Summer}} <br> [[Austin Clapp]]<br>[[Philip Daubenspeck]]<br>[[Charles Finn]]<br>[[Charles McCallister]]<br>[[Wally O'Connor]]<br>[[Cal Strong]]<br>[[Herbert Wildman]]\n|}\n\n==Weightlifting==\n{{main|Weightlifting at the 1932 Summer Olympics}}\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event}}\n|-\n|Featherweight<br/><span style=\"font-size:90%\">''\u201360&nbsp;kg''</span> {{DetailsLink|Weightlifting at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 60 kg}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Raymond Suvigny]]|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Hans W\u00f6lpert]]|GER|1932 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Anthony Terlazzo]]|USA|1932 Summer}}\n|-\n|Lightweight<br/><span style=\"font-size:90%\">''\u201367.5&nbsp;kg''</span> {{DetailsLink|Weightlifting at the 1932 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 67.5 kg}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Ren\u00e9 Duverger]]|FRA|1932 Summer}}\n|{{